name: Standard Home Cleaning
description: Comprehensive home cleaning service including dusting, vacuuming, mopping, bathroom cleaning, kitchen cleaning, and bed making. Perfect for regular maintenance of your living space.

name: Deep Home Cleaning
description: Thorough deep cleaning service that includes everything in the standard cleaning plus inside appliance cleaning, cabinet organization, window washing, and detailed attention to high-touch surfaces and hard-to-reach areas.

name: Women's Haircut & Style
description: Professional women's haircut and styling service. Includes consultation, shampoo, conditioning treatment, precision cut, blow dry, and styling according to your preferences.

name: Manicure & Pedicure Combo
description: Luxurious nail care package including both manicure and pedicure. Service includes nail shaping, cuticle care, exfoliation, massage, and polish application of your choice.

name: Smartphone Screen Replacement
description: Professional smartphone screen replacement service for all major brands including Apple, Samsung, Google, and more. Service includes diagnostics, replacement of screen assembly, and testing.

name: Computer Virus Removal & Optimization
description: Comprehensive computer malware removal and system optimization service. Includes virus scanning, malware removal, system cleanup, software updates, and performance optimization.

name: Move-In/Move-Out Cleaning
description: Specialized cleaning service for moving situations. Thorough cleaning of empty property including all surfaces, appliances, cabinets, closets, fixtures, and flooring to prepare for new occupants or to secure deposit return.

name: Facial Treatment
description: Rejuvenating facial treatment customized to your skin type. Includes cleansing, exfoliation, extraction, mask, serum application, and moisturizing. Helps improve skin texture, tone, and overall appearance.
